snippet.title: Watch Sky News live
snippet.description:
Watch Sky News live. Today's top stories: The father of Arthur Labinjo-Hughes and his girlfriend have been jailed for the six-year-old's killing; another 75 cases of the Omicron COVID variant have been found in England, the UK Health Security Agency has said; and involuntary manslaughter charges have been filed against the parents of a 15-year-old accused of killing four students and wounding seven others at a Michigan school.

Three stories you should read today:

🔴 Arthur Labinjo-Hughes: Father and girlfriend jailed for 'inhuman' killing of six-year-old boy https://trib.al/czrJzjH
🔴 Another 75 cases of the Omicron COVID variant have been found in England, the UK Health Security Agency has said https://trib.al/OQJ4fDp
🔴 Michigan school shooting: Ethan Crumbley's parents charged with involuntary manslaughter https://trib.al/bk8iyfn
